00:11:50.770 --> 00:11:53.380
You know the rules, right?

250
00:11:53.410 --> 00:11:55.900
You know the rules of the method.
Very simple.

251
00:11:55.920 --> 00:11:59.860
You may continue to the next section when
you're able to answer all the questions

252
00:11:59.890 --> 00:12:03.300
in the interactive version correctly.

253
00:12:03.330 --> 00:12:06.917
So "yes", "no", "yes", "no", "yes",
correctly.

254
00:12:07.117 --> 00:12:10.713
Every single answer correct,
out loud, on time

255
00:12:10.913 --> 00:12:13.620
and without looking at the transcript.

256
00:12:13.650 --> 00:12:14.780
Okay?
Great.

257
00:12:14.810 --> 00:12:17.420
And remember, input creates output.
Be patient.

258
00:12:17.450 --> 00:12:18.660
Be patient.
Right?

259
00:12:18.680 --> 00:12:21.940
The more you listen, the more you read,
the more you consume the language,

260
00:12:21.960 --> 00:12:24.300
the better you will speak,
the better you will write.

261
00:12:24.330 --> 00:12:27.260
But speaking and writing takes time, okay?

262
00:12:27.280 --> 00:12:30.260
Your listening is always going
to be better than your speaking.

263
00:12:30.280 --> 00:12:33.100
Your reading is always going
to be better than your writing.

264
00:12:33.130 --> 00:12:35.700
That is just how language learning works.

265
00:12:35.730 --> 00:12:39.820
Accept it and keep working on more input,
more and more and more,

266
00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:43.260
so that you internalize the vocabulary
and grammar structures in your longterm

267
00:12:43.290 --> 00:12:48.660
memory, which is the cause
of being able to produce output.

268
00:12:48.690 --> 00:12:50.820
Right?
Okay, great.

269
00:12:50.850 --> 00:12:51.540
And remember,

270
00:12:51.570 --> 00:12:56.000
you can practice conversations with other
students and a conversation facilitator

271
00:12:56.030 --> 00:12:57.898
in the RAIO Conversation Club.

272
00:12:58.098 --> 00:12:59.580
If you have specific needs,

273
00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:01.260
if you want to accelerate your learning

274
00:13:01.290 --> 00:13:05.420
and get a private coach just for you, you
can join RAIO Premium and get that too.

275
00:13:05.450 --> 00:13:07.740
More information in section number 18.

276
00:13:07.770 --> 00:13:10.060
But for now, just keep
going with the method.

277
00:13:10.080 --> 00:13:11.300
You know what to do.

278
00:13:11.330 --> 00:13:13.924
But before you move on, please repeat
after me.

279
00:13:14.124 --> 00:13:19.320
"I'll become fluent in English.
I'll never give up on my goal."

280
00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:24.420
Awesome.

281
00:13:24.450 --> 00:13:25.580
Okay, great job.

282
00:13:25.610 --> 00:13:28.460
Now, let's get started,
and I'll see you in the next one.

283
00:13:28.490 --> 00:13:29.120
Bye!

